name: TOXIC WORLD ONE
description: Digitally altered photograph. 4928px by 3264px (240 ppi). 2112 A.D. Most of the world population has been killed by a pandemic which origins remain unknown. The rare survivors face a harsh reality--scarce food and potable water, toxic fumes and mutant animals and insects, increasingly intelligent and aggressive, which have taken over the most unexpected places. Will humanity survive?
